News.headline: Match Rescheduled: Lincoln City v Dagenham and Redbridge
News.page_title: Match Rescheduled: Lincoln City v Dagenham and Redbridge
News.URL_keywords: Match Rescheduled: Lincoln City v Dagenham and Redbridge
News.short_description: Due to Lincoln City being involved in the Buildbase FA Trophy fifth round, our away tie at Sincil Bank has been rescheduled for Tuesday 4th April, 7:45pm KO.
News.description: Any ticket information from Lincoln City for this game will be announced at a later date.
